query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(s t tq) NoHashJoin(s t tq q) */ select count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t
on t.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('wordpress') AND t.name IN ('custom-post-types',
'php',
'plugins')
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND tq.site_id = s.site_id
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000;
